nodes.text: Phoenix Six was a callsign used by Phoenix Squadron, an A-wing squadron that was a part of the early rebellion against the Galactic Empire. Lieutenant Dicer served as Phoenix Six shortly after the rebels established a base on the planet Atollon.
Kay Karno used the callsign of Phoenix Six during a dogfight against TIE/ln space superiority starfighters, when her RZ-1 A-wing interceptor was damaged.
